latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Skincare w/ @sadhev , Skincare is a crucial part of my everyday routine and while looking for all natural & organic products I came across this beautiful Ayurvedic Skincare Brand @sadhev which creates Skincare products made of ayurvedic oils & Natural ingredients. I got my hands on their Ayurvedic Cleanser for sensitive skin and I am obsessed with how it felt on my skin , super mild and non fragrant left my skin supple and dirt free without making it stretchy or dry. I definitely can’t wait to try more products from Sadhev and I would highly suggest Sadhev to you guys as well.

#SkincareWithSadhev

Hello Glowy skin ✨ // My new found love is this 24K Gold Radiance Brightening Face Elixir from @rasluxuryoils, it not only brightens & smoothens but also hydrates and reduces pigmentation. I use it everyday to moisturise my skin, use it as a primer and on top of my base makeup for a dewy look.

latestIgtvVideos.title: 2 go to hairstyles ft. @dyson_india Airwrap
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have always been extremely particular about how my hair looks and always struggled to find the perfect hairstyling tool but I got my hands on  @dyson_india ‘s Airwrap which helps me achieve salon like hair at home and I've never looked back!  It comes with multiple attachments which help groom and style the hair in various ways. The tool according to me is an investment. I can now easily achieve salon like blow dried hair at home with zero heat damage to my hair. In this video I tried two different hairstyles and I absolutely love both of them! Hope you like the video too, please let me know which look you'd be trying? 
#GoodbyeExtremeHeat
#DysonIndia
#DysonAirwrap

latestIgtvVideos.title: Avoid critical situation in covid19 patients.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In the past few days I’ve learnt a lot about COVID-19 with my personal experience and with the help of @dr.sarahgery and I really wanted to let out whatever information I know to spread awareness. Have seen so many people loosing their lives and their loved ones and this is the least I could do, I hope few of you find this video useful and it could be of any help to you guys. 
Disclaimer: please consult your doctor as he is going to suggest you the right treatment and Please be kind and correct if I am wrong 🙏🏻🤍 #InThisTogther
